      "content": "Hey, so I'm working on some market research for a new skincare line that's trying to launch globally. We're trying to get a handle on what actually defines 'beauty' nowadays. From a professional standpoint, do you think there's a set of facial features or characteristics that are pretty much universally seen as the most desirable or attractive, or is it strictly different in every region?",
